      "announcements": [
        {
          "content": "Azure Official Image Generation Model: gpt-image-2-official is now live with token-based pricing; existing gpt-image-2 remains on per-request pricing.",
          "extra": "已上线 Azure 官方生图模型 gpt-image-2-official，按 Token 计费；原有 gpt-image-2 继续按次计费，保持不变。",
          "id": 9,
          "publishDate": "2026-06-09T02:18:19.059Z",
          "type": "success"
        },
        {
          "content": "Nbility now supports the seedance-2-480p and seedance-2-720p pay-per-second models, as well as face recognition and skip-the-line features. See  [seedance 2.0 docs](https://nbility.dev/docs/api/videos/seedance) to get start.",
          "extra": "Nbility 已支持邀请充值返佣；已上架 seedance-2-480p、seedance-2-720p 按秒计费模型，支持人脸、免排队。",
          "id": 8,
          "publishDate": "2026-05-19T14:13:49.627Z",
          "type": "success"
        },
        {
          "content": "Images are stored on CDN for 3 days. Grab the URL from your generation log and download promptly.",
          "extra": "图片生成后会在 CDN 中保存 3 天，可在生图日志详情中获取图片地址，请及时下载。",
          "id": 3,
          "publishDate": "2026-05-11T03:51:39.000Z",
          "type": "default"
        },
        {
          "content": "For gpt-image-2 models, async mode is recommended for higher success rates. See the [API docs](https://nbility.dev/docs/api/images) for details. Please implement client-side retry logic. Note that high-res / high-quality modes have higher latency and lower success rates.",
          "extra": "调用 gpt-image-2 相关模型时，高分辨率、高质量模式延迟较高，出图成功率较低。若失败，请在客户端自行实现重试逻辑。",
          "id": 2,
          "publishDate": "2026-05-10T03:49:03.000Z",
          "type": "warning"
        },
        {
          "content": "Nbility now supports gpt-5.5 and gpt-image-2. API docs: https://nbility.dev/docs/api/images",
          "extra": "Nbility 已支持 gpt-5.5、gpt-image-2。API 文档：https://nbility.dev/docs/api/images",
          "id": 4,
          "publishDate": "2026-04-24T03:52:11.000Z",
          "type": "success"
        },
        {
          "content": "Nbility is officially launched, with support for Codex, Claude Code, and Gemini.\n\nNbility 正式发布，支持 Codex、Claude Code、Gemini。Nbility 的目标不是做大做强，而是各位朋友、家人们能在有需要的时候，能方便、快捷的用上这些AI工具，感受技术对工作、生活的改变，哪怕你不常用，在下次突然想起这个工具时，打开敲下回车，Nbility 依然给予你最快捷的回复！",
          "extra": "",
          "id": 5,
